{"instruction": "欧拉方程 $x^{2} y^{\\prime \\prime}+x y^{\\prime}-4 y=0$ 满足条件 $y(1)=1, y^{\\prime}(1)=2$ 得解为 $y=$", "input": "", "output": "令 $x=e^{t}$, 则 $x y^{\\prime}=\\frac{d y}{d t}, x^{2} y^{\\prime \\prime}=\\frac{d^{2} y}{d x^{2}}-\\frac{d y}{d x}$, 原方程化为 $\\frac{d^{2} y}{d x^{2}}-4 y=0$, 特征方程为 $\\lambda^{2}-4=0$, 特征根为 $\\lambda_{1}=2, \\lambda_{2}=-2$, 通解为 $y=C_{1} e^{2 t}+C_{2} e^{-2 t}=C_{1} x^{2}+C_{2} x^{-2}$, 将初始条件 $y(1)=1, y^{\\prime}(1)=2$ 带入得 $C_{1}=1, C_{2}=0$, 故满足初始条件的解为 $y=x^{2}$.\n因此答案为: $x^{2}$", "task_type": {"major": ["试题"], "minor": ["考研", "填空题"]}, "domain": ["数学"], "metadata": "year:2021, score:5", "answer_from": "human", "human_verified": false, "copyright": "暂无版权及作者信息"}


